text: Agdistis olei is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Iran, Oman, Bahrain, Saudi Arabia and the United Arab Emirates.A new species, a new synonym, and new distribution records in the genus Agdistis Hübner, 1825 from Iran (Pterophoridae: Agdistinae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of the Arabian Peninsula Category:Moths described in 1976
title: Agdistis olei
